<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.4">
<l>maccaṇi māṭa matiḷaraṅkar vāmaṉaṉār</l>
<l>paccaip pacuntēvar tāmpaṇṭu nīrēṟṟa</l>
<l>piccaik kuṟaiyāki yeṉṉuṭaiya peyvaḷaimē</l>
<l>liccai yuṭaiyarē litteruvē pōtārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He from Raṅgam with mansions adorned with upper storeys and ramparts,</l>
<l>the honourable Vāmana, the deep green[-hued] Lord had a lack</l>
<l>with regards to the alms that He previously received with water.</l>
<l>If [as a result, He] desires my bangles that I have put on, won’t He come on this street?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
